<paragraph blockId="26.[151,1437,150,393]" pageId="26" pageNumber="477">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[199,262,222,248]" pageId="26" pageNumber="477">Note.</emphasis>
Full bibliography for this species covering complicated historical and nomenclatural issues with application of two names 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Menetries" authorityYear="1832" box="[360,517,258,284]" class="Insecta" family="Tenebrionidae" genus="Helops" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="26" pageNumber="477" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="quadraticollis">
<emphasis box="[360,517,258,284]" italics="true" pageId="26" pageNumber="477">quadraticollis</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
/ 
<taxonomicName baseAuthorityName="Menetries" baseAuthorityYear="1832" box="[540,675,258,284]" class="Insecta" family="Tenebrionidae" genus="Euboeus" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="26" pageNumber="477" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="quadricollis">
<emphasis box="[540,675,258,284]" italics="true" pageId="26" pageNumber="477">quadricollis</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
for this species, discussion about the author of the taxon, as well as short redescription and figures were published by 
<bibRefCitation author="Abdurakhmanov, G. M. &amp; Nabozhenko, M. V." box="[710,1159,294,320]" pageId="26" pageNumber="477" refId="ref21743" refString="Abdurakhmanov, G. M. &amp; Nabozhenko, M. V. (2011) Keys and catalogue to darkling beetles (Coleoptera: Tenebrionidae s. str.) of the Caucasus and south of European part of Russia. KMK Scientific Press Ltd, Moscow, 361 pp. [in Russian]" type="book" year="2011">Abdurakhmanov &amp; Nabozhenko (2011)</bibRefCitation>
